<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>11128</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24189</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个道士把唐僧推到那口巨大的油锅旁。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24190</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“住手！”悟空大叫。道士停下了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>36369</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙四处看了看。悟空出现并落在地上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>36370</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>40242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你回来了！”唐僧大叫。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>40243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43530</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我一直就在这儿。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43531</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49689</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他讨厌地看了八戒一眼：“我不会扔下你们逃走的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49690</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53920</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空转身对着镇元大仙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53921</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>57162</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“请不要伤害我师父。”他说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>57163</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>61783</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会救活你的人参果树，但我需要帮助。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>61784</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>68662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他在撒谎！”八戒说，“他根本不知道怎么救活那棵树！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>68663</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>73665</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“安静，八戒！”悟空说，“我没撒谎！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>73666</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79661</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>镇元大仙想了一会：“好的，悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79662</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>86778</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我给你时间，你要在今天之内把我的人参果树救活。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>86779</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>91450</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>如果你做不到，唐僧就要进油锅。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>91451</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>98047</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧害怕得浑身发抖。“不用担心，师父。”悟空说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>98048</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101790</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我会找到人帮忙的。我尽快回来。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101791</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>105505</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空迅速离开了道观。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>105506</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>110161</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒摇摇头：“我们这次完了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>110162</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空一路腾云驾雾，一直到了普陀山。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨正在那里冥想。“观音菩萨！”悟空大叫，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124516</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>131321</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我需要您的帮助！一个名叫镇元大仙的道士要炸了唐僧。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>131322</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135724</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>今天之内我必须要救活他的人参果树。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135725</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143289</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那树怎么了？”观音菩萨问。她怀疑地看了看悟空。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143290</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>148446</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我，嗯，我把它弄倒了。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>148447</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>154242</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你这样做太可恶了，悟空。”观音菩萨说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>154243</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161789</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“镇元大仙的人参果树比天地都要老。那是个少见的宝贝。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161790</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165916</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空耸耸肩：“我当时很生气。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165917</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>171528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你必须学会控制你的脾气。”观音菩萨说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>171529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨站了起来。她走到一个架子前面拿起了净瓶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182704</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“这净瓶里装的是甘露。”她说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182705</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>189960</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它可以令那些有灵的植物，比如那棵人参果树起死回生。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>189961</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>197893</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>过了没多久，悟空就和观音菩萨一起到了道观。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>197894</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206173</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨让悟空、八戒和悟净将人参果树扶起来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206174</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>213358</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>观音菩萨升到空中把甘露倒在了人参果树上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>213359</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>219443</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>甘露顺着树枝滚动，闪闪发光。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>219444</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>226998</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>那树的颜色又变回来了，还长出了新的叶子和果子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>226999</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>232431</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>很快那树就和以前一模一样了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>232432</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>238320</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>为了感谢所有人，镇元大仙决定举行宴会。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>238321</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>244448</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我要和在座的各位分享人参果。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>244449</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>247465</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>所有人都回到了道观里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>247466</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>255184</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个道士用托盘装来了人参果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>255185</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263894</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“嗯。”八戒说，“这果子如果慢慢吃的话，味道确实很好。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263895</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>269910</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他看着悟空：“对不起，我之前没有相信你。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>269911</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>275760</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“别想那件事儿了。”悟空说。他咬了一口人参果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>275761</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>279896</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧紧张地看着他的人参果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>279897</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284727</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“吃这个没事的。”观音菩萨向他保证。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284728</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>290851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>唐僧咬了一口，笑了。他又看了看人参果。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>290852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>295183</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“它看上去不再像个婴儿了。”他说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>295184</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301847</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>第二天一早，这一行人继续沿着大路向西走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301848</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们又继续走了几个星期。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>314891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们一路风雨无阻，无论严寒酷暑。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>314892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>322238</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>前方，有个名叫白骨精的妖精坐在路边。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>322239</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>328166</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她一直在路边等着，已经等了好几年了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>328167</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>336932</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这一天她在空气中闻了闻，然后笑了：“唐僧就要到了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>336933</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>345891</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要吃了他，然后我就可以长生不老了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>